recipeIngredient: 348g Old El Paso Stand â€™n Stuff Soft Taco Kit

recipeInstructions.text: Heat 1 tbs extra virgin olive oil in a large frying pan over medium-high heat. Add mince and cook, breaking up lumps with a wooden spoon, for 5 minutes or until well browned. Add seasoning from kit and 1/2 cup water, then cook, stirring, for 3 minutes or until fragrant.
Add half of the tomato to beef mixture and cook, stirring occasionally, for 5 minutes or until tomato starts to soften and mixture has thickened.
Meanwhile, heat tacos according to packet instructions.
Fill each taco with baby leaf salad, beef mixture and remaining tomatoes. Serve with salsa from kit.
